Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:47.09,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛情×友情　想い重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:50.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たいせつを奏でよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:14.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うれしくって泣いた　痛くって笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:23.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどそんな全部が生きてる証なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:27.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ゆっくり歩いていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.29,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:33.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとさじの本音　聞かせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:41.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛情×友情　時に揺れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:41.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I know, You know little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:46.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっとずっと　響きあいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:46.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:52.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ありふれてる言葉では伝えきれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:58.74,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちのHarmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:03.78,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}聴こえる　our Harmony
Comment: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:47.09,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱情×友情  堆积层层思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:50.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吹响心爱的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:14.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}时而喜极而泣  时而忍痛大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:23.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如此日常点滴  尽是活着真我风采
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:27.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}缓缓迈步向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:33.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}让我倾听你的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:41.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱情×友情  即使被时光动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:46.98,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永远  永远  响彻你我心间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:52.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}日常琐碎的平淡话语无法尽诉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:58.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们的和声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:03.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}定能听见  我们的和声
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那你是密史特拉来的啊  真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们那东西好吃  美女也多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停战以来快有半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能活着看到这天真是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  J
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  怎能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战利品  分你点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能  能收到如此贵重之物  感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  军曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦  据说只要能和司号兵拉近关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就总能顺利的听到撤退的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经不征兵了  竟然还能看到新兵  真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了学习音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说出来很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵  你名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫空深彼方
