Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞兹今天正过节日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节日？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能送你到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的分派地  俗称「晓时堡」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着那里前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命  空深彼方  二等兵  到特鲁瓦州的塞兹  1121小队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫尔维西亚共和国陆军总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1320  任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖泊和玻璃的城市  塞兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报道时间是1500
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能够让你歌唱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向检查  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻检查  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装备检查  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前起步  走！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降G调  美丽的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,￥10.25  哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊  好漂亮的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只沉浸在节日气氛里的小猫  向错误的方向疾奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所当然的嘛  小猫就是爱乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是野猫的话还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜  那是家猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}喂  拿到这边一下…快快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过又发现了另一种美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  军官小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是碉堡的少女吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了「火焰」  谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你给我泼的  瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗  跟着闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄成那一副样子打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跟我来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温还合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个好靶子啊  不知道躲闪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种染料干后是不会留下痕渍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是节日活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是源自塞兹的传说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说？  什么样的传说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女  守护城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你费神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你记下的  那边的修理也完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利西娅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个多管闲事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢  真慢  真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还亏我特意来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  慢慢地等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸给你的礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降D调
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢款待泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我不知为何总是迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也因此我才能遇到这么好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在这里可不要迷路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依稀  有一种怀旧的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在问那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要为了那种东西死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那个铃铛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是  就这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要出门  别再迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个铃铛  一定很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远在世界变成现在的模样之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城镇的山谷底下住着一只长翅膀的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔口吐烈焰  摇撼大地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使人们陷入痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着  恶魔掠走住在碉堡里的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她们关在地下迷宫里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  少女们并不言弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用天主大人授予的金色角笛互相呼应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃离迷宫后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助巨大蜘蛛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败恶魔  并刎下其首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随即  那颗头颅喷出炽热的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  山谷上的城镇就要化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女们为了制止喷出的烈焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮流地抱住恶魔的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着燃烧的恶魔头颅以及少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们日复一日地泼水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年之后火焰终于消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来  为了慰藉拯救城镇的少女们的英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便设立了这个泼水节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来啊  新人小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随她去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看看  队长  梨旺前辈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  跟她很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给她果然是正确选择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是抽签…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然迷路有时会是件快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是因为能和陌生的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独一人  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  只要你这么希望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能传达想要相见的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音一定会响起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会响起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会响起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  传达出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之少女  于此沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱恶魔  镇其诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈愿永无觉醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色角笛  难道恶魔醒来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有人  听到我的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音一定会响起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点起床  空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是晓时堡  1121小队的驻扎地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑  但是再也别乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这么一个铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这座要塞会称作晓时堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宫梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将在号手方面指导你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教  梨旺曹长殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫梨旺就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是菲利西娅  队长的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不分军阶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么  梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床号  吹一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的孩子吹得真难听
Comment: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
